[l] Paul Craig Roberts erklaert die US-Militaerdoktrin. Seine Zusammenfassung:Pentagon Concludes America Not Safe Unless It Conquers The WorldWer ist Paul Craig Roberts? Wikipedia sagt:He served as an assistant secretary of the treasury for economic policy in the Reagan administration. He is a former editor and columnist for the Wall Street Journal, Business Week, and Scripps Howard News Service. (Danke, Florian)
